titles.title: To name the Department of Veterans Affairs outpatient clinic in Aiken, South Carolina, as the "Matthew V. Dillon Department of Veterans Affairs Outpatient Clinic".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Veterans' Affairs.

bill.summary:
12/11/2007--Introduced.
Designates the Department of Veterans Affairs Outpatient Clinic in Aiken, South Carolina, as the "Matthew V. Dillon Department of Veterans Affairs Outpatient Clinic."
